content: Can you explain what observable? click on the link for full question https://qr.ae/pKbuTN. Observables can be created using operators like of, from, or by transforming existing data structures into observables. Subscribers can then subscribe to these observables to receive and react to emitted values. This subscription mechanism allows components and services to stay informed about changes in the application's state.
